[soft music]

01:19.113 --> 01:20.908
- He was wearing
like this really

01:20.942 --> 01:23.600
stupid orange camouflage shirt.

01:25.119 --> 01:27.397
- That's good, Becky.

01:27.432 --> 01:29.089
And do you remember
what happened

01:29.123 --> 01:32.609
to the man in the
orange camouflage shirt?

01:36.303 --> 01:39.133
[heavy breathing]

01:40.341 --> 01:43.172
- What happened by
your fort, Becky?

01:46.278 --> 01:47.314
- [Man] Help.

01:53.458 --> 01:54.459
- I'm sorry.

01:56.978 --> 01:58.256
I don't know.

01:58.290 --> 02:00.637
[soft music]

02:13.167 --> 02:15.721
[bright music]

02:22.003 --> 02:27.008
